谢谢

308
00:21:45,670 --> 00:21:50,730
Chandler, your being here is the best Christmas present I could ever imagine.
钱德，你能够在这里 是我有过最棒的圣诞礼物了

309
00:21:52,270 --> 00:21:54,760
- Now give me my real gift. - Yeah.
-现在给我真正的礼物 -好

310
00:21:54,940 --> 00:21:57,000
- Thank you. - Here, pass those around.
-谢谢 -这里，分给大家

311
00:22:05,390 --> 00:22:09,690
"A donation has been made in your name to the New York City Ballet."
“一项捐款已经以您的名义 捐赠给纽约市立芭蕾舞团”

312
00:22:11,430 --> 00:22:13,760
How did you know?
你怎么会知道我要这个呢？

313
00:22:13,930 --> 00:22:17,920
What? Are you kidding? I can't return this.
什么？你在开玩笑吗？ 我不能退还这个的

314
00:22:19,100 --> 00:22:21,290
It's time we started thinking about other people.
该是我们关怀别人的时候了

315
00:22:21,470 --> 00:22:24,100
And besides, this gift still says, "I love you guys."
除此之外，这份礼物还包含了 “我爱你们”

316
00:22:24,300 --> 00:22:28,100
- Mine says, "To Lillian Myers." - I don't have a job.
-我的上面写“给莉莉安迈尔” -我可是失业了

317
00:22:32,980 --> 00:22:35,570
Actuary? No.
精算师？不

318
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:39,080
Bookkeeper? No.
簿记员？不

319
00:22:39,250 --> 00:22:41,850
Topless dancer?
上空舞者？

320
00:22:47,260 --> 00:22:50,790
Hey, you know what I just realized? You are the sole wage earner.
嗨，你知道我刚刚才想通什么吗？ 你是家里唯一收入来源

321
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:56,460
You are the head of the household. I don't do anything. I'm a kept man!
你是这个家的户长 我什么都没做，我是被供养的小白脸！

322
00:22:56,670 --> 00:22:58,160
You are.
没错

323
00:22:58,370 --> 00:22:59,770
Honey, here's 20 bucks.
亲爱的，这里有二十块

324
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:02,670
Go buy yourself something pretty while I'm at work tomorrow.
我明天去上班的时候 你去买一些漂亮的东西

